data.title: North Bondi Fish
data.meta_description: North Bondi Fish offers seafood meals and a relaxed vibe located on a world-famous beach, perfect for lunch, dinner and anything in between. Visit us today!
data.text:
You're invited to sip away and play at NBF this winter.

All your favourite NBF classics are on our a la carte menu, think fish tacos, fresh sashimi and killer seasonal margaritas. There are some new additions too, like an ‘Australian Bay lobster’ slider, ½ kg mussel pot with chorizo, chilli and fries, a delicious NBF fish & prawn pie. For something sweet, dig into our Pink Lady apple crumble topped with vanilla ice cream.

Our takeaway menu is the perfect curation of iconic seaside bites including our NBF Fish Burger, Fish & Chips, plus seriously fresh options including our Poke Bowl. There's something delicious for everyone. Check out the menu below to order now.
